author: Brent K
title: Brent K
text: I'm unsure if I read the item incorrectly or what exactly caused the issue, but I was expecting an insufflator bulb for an otoscope and received a bulb to pump up blood pressure cuffs. I'm fairly certain the wording implied I was purchasing the right item and the image appeared to be what I was expecting, however what came in the mail was something else.
